definitions.definition: ( also attributively ) A competitive game in which the objective is to flick as many small discs (each called a tiddlywink or wink ) as possible into a container (the pot ) by pressing on their edges with a larger disc (a shooter or squidger ), causing them to jump up from the surface on which they are placed .
( figuratively ) Especially in the form to play tiddlywinks : a meaningless or unimportant activity .
